 us had heard of their big rock hit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s2\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;&amp;ldquo;Way Home&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s2\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;&amp;rdquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;- being played in endless radio stations. The band itself has been actively travelling around and play big concerts all around the globe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegi