 playing the guitar&amp;nbsp;made him famous in a short period of time.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=\"s1\"&gt;His one big dream: touring around the United States.&amp;nbsp;In 2016 he is as close as never before – with his new album, reaching records in the US.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-background#3\" sv:type=\"Boolean\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"0\">0</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-type#4\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"4\">text</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-text#4\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"405\">&lt;p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Genre:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Folk&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Label:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;International Talents &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Current Members:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Jack &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Active:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;2012 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Website:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;coyoo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-background#4\" sv:type=\"Boolean\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"0\">0</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-type#5\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"19\">discography_element</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-discographyTitle#5\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"5\">Album</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-discographyData#5\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"196\">{\"dataSource\":\"1393bf7c-6af7-437d-85b7-e8b88f8937c1\",\"includeSubFolders\":false,\"categories\":[],\"ca