al-align: baseline;\"&gt;TJ Fury, the new Hip Hop star&amp;nbsp;was already a famous musican even before most of us had heard of his legendary song - &amp;quot;nevertheless&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s2\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;- being played in endless radio stations. TJ Fury has been actively travelling around and play &amp;nbsp;all around the globe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;From there beginning he was&amp;nbsp;signed to International Talents in 2003, you could say they were&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;ready to make a big step to the entrance to the big stage&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;his&amp;nbsp;debut album &amp;lsquo;down_town&amp;rsquo;. In a relatively short time, TJ Fury has&amp;nbsp;an&amp;nbsp;impact with their tracks&amp;nbsp;in all countries from Asia to the United States.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;The Album down_town&amp;nbsp;is released in May 2016. Recorded between his citytrips&amp;nbsp;in 2014 and 2015. His album was&amp;nbsp; primarily produced by himself. &amp;nbsp;It was mastered by Dave Richardson. According to TJ Fury, the album took three years to finish. Musically this new Album contains and combained nuances of pop, and Hip Hop.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;Before the release of the new album down_town, he&amp;nbsp;took the chance and played more and more songs on his world Tour. The 25-date&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s2\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;&amp;bdquo;US-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;City Tour 2015&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s2\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=\"s1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"&gt;, featuring&amp;nbsp; newcomer stars as opening act, saw TJ Fury travel across the United States. During the tour, more and more songs rised and a new album appeared in the end of the long US Tour.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 22px; font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(49, 49, 49);\"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\