 week and they have already played half a dozend concerts.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=\"p1\"&gt;You\'re watching and thinking, \"the show\'s true magic and their performace is amazing\", that\'s how famous music critic Joe Zipotta descriped the show in Amsterdam. \"It seems like in the last three year the band has improved a lot and wrote some awesome songs. Especially the frontman Liam was fascinating, he managed it to take the visitors in a other world. It was truely terrific.\"&lt;/p&gt;\n</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-background#1\" sv:type=\"Boolean\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"0\">0</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-type#2\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"5\">quote</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-quote#2\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"115\">The first week is over and is\'s so great!\n\nGermany and the Netherlands, Berlin and Amsterdam, tour live is awesome!</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-background#2\" sv:type=\"Boolean\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"0\">0</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-type#3\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"4\">text</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-text#3\" sv:type=\"String\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"296\">&lt;p&gt;Civil Literatures concerts in Germany and the Netherlands are already over, but there will be a lot of other opportunities to see them and hear their extra ordanary&amp;nbsp;new songs.&amp;nbsp;The next stops are Paris and London. After Europe Civil Literature will then play in America and Asia.&lt;/p&gt;\n</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-background#3\" sv:type=\"Boolean\" sv:multi-valued=\"0\"><sv:value length=\"0\">0</sv:value></sv:property><sv:property sv:name=\"i18n:en-blocks-type#4\" sv:type=